2:T746,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Otter.ai better than Podcastle?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Otter.ai scores 8.0 overall while Podcastle scores 7.0. Otter.ai is best for meeting transcription and journalists and students, while Podcastle excels for podcast creators and audio content production."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Otter.ai or Podcastle?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Otter.ai starts at $8.33/mo and Podcastle starts at $11.99/mo. Otter.ai offers a free plan. Podcastle offers a free plan. Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Otter.ai to Podcastle?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Otter.ai and Podcastle support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Otter.ai vs Podcastle?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Otter.ai holds an overall rating of 8/10 and an ease of use score of 9/10. Podcastle has an overall rating of 7/10 and ease of use score of 8/10. Users praise Otter.ai for excellent real-time transcription and Podcastle for all-in-one podcast studio."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Otter.ai or Podcastle?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Otter.ai for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Podcastle remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize all-in-one podcast studio. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"oWPZTPCPUwZMl312gxRMA","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerousl